snippet.title: Leaked found video footage. Baisu - Horror Game Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the shoes of Detective Clay Kriest in "Baisu," a chilling tale of family, art, and the haunting unknown. As you arrive at the secluded residence of Maple Street 22, responding to an eerie call for help, you'll find yourself immersed in a quest shrouded in darkness.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2821850/Baisu/
